org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.driver.js

Class JSCompilationUnit

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICompilationUnit

    public class JSCompilationUnit
extends ASCompilationUnit
    JSCompilationUnit is the CompilationUnit for compiling ActionScript source files to JavasScript.

    JSCompilationUnit is derived from ASCompilationUnit and overrides the parts that generate the code.
